description.en: The Urban Energy Simulation ontology is designed to facilitate the handling and organisation of heterogeneous data used in urban building energy modelling. The ontology contains a standardised vocabulary that, when implemented into a linked graph database, overcomes some of the main challenges regarding data availability, accuracy and traceability.
